race.description: Great Northern Brewing Co Maiden Handicap
race.comment: MISS KIYOSHI (14) was in the betting when over this track and trip on debut but just missed the placings on that occasion. Will have taken a bunch of benefit from that race day experience and where there's smoke there's fire. Can improve enough to take this out. Former NSW galloper MIND OVER MATTER (13) is having his first run for the new stable but should find this easier than what he faced down south. Looks well placed against this line-up. STORM CAPITAL (3) strips fitter third-up from the spell and gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Shapes among the leading players. ROCK ON ANGEL (10) has placed two from three over this sprint journey and may make her presence felt. MIDDLE CHILD (9) wasn't too far away when having her first run for the new barn and can feature with natural improvement.
